    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击加沙清真寺致 19 人死亡；对贝鲁特的轰炸加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-apparent-israeli-airstrike-on-mosque-in-central-gaza-kills-at-least-18-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代尔巴拉，加沙地带（美联社）——周日晚间，新一轮空袭袭击了贝鲁特郊区，以色列加强了对加沙北部和黎巴嫩南部的轰炸，与该地区与伊朗结盟的武装团体的战争不断扩大。巴勒斯坦官员称，对一座清真寺的袭击造成至少 19 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-apparent-israeli-airstrike-on-mosque-in-central-gaza-kills-at-least-18-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 04:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
